    "title": "Wafilisti",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "wafilisti",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Wafilisti waliishi kwenye uwanda wa pwani ya kusini mashariki mwa Bahari ya Mediterania. Walikuwa sehemu ya kundi kubwa la wasafiri wa baharini kutoka eneo la Aegean, ambao Wamisri waliwaita &quot;Watu wa Baharini.&quot; Karibu mwaka wa 1200 Kabla ya Kristo (KK), walikaa kwenye uwanda wa chini wa pwani ya Palestina na kuanzisha miji mitano:</p><ol><li><p>Ashdodi</p></li><li><p>Ashkeloni</p></li><li><p>Ekroni</p></li><li><p>Gaza</p></li><li><p>Gathi</p></li></ol><p>Wafilisti hawakuwa rahisi kushinda; walikuwa na ujuzi katika siasa na teknolojia. Walikuwa pia wapiganaji hodari. Teknolojia yao ya chuma iliwafanya kuwa maadui karibu wasioshindika (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:19-1Sam13:22\">1 Samweli 13:19–22</a>). Mara nyingi walipigana na Waisraeli wakati wa Waamuzi, karibu mwaka wa 1350 hadi 1050 KK, na wakati wa ufalme wa kwanza ulio unganishwa, kutoka takriban mwaka wa 1050 hadi 970 KK. Sauli alikufa akipigana na Wafilisti (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam31:1-1Sam31:13\">1 Samweli 31:1–13</a>). Hata hivyo, Daudi aliwashinda kabla hajawa mfalme (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:20-1Sam18:30\">1 Samweli 18:20–30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:8\">19:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:1-1Sam23:5\">23:1–5</a>) na aliendelea kuwashinda wakati wa utawala wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:17-2Sam5:25\">2 Samweli 5:17–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:1\">8:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:15\">21:15–22</a>). Ingawa Wafilisti hawakuwahi kutoweka kabisa wakati Israeli ilikuwepo kama taifa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:8\">2 Wafalme 18:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:11\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:16-2Chr21:17\">21:16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:6-2Chr26:7\">26:6–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:18\">28:18</a>), Daudi alimaliza tishio lao kwa ufanisi.</p><p>Kwenye 1 Samweli, Mungu alitumia Wafilisti kuondoa familia ya Eli yenye dhambi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:10-1Sam4:22\">1 Samweli 4:10–22</a>). Wafilisti pia walichangia katika kujenga nguvu za kijeshi na kisiasa za Daudi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:32-1Sam17:58\">1 Samweli 17:32–58</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:20-1Sam18:30\">18:20–30</a>). Walimvuruga Sauli alipokuwa karibu kumkamata Daudi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:26-1Sam23:28\">1 Samweli 23:26–28</a>). Walimpa Daudi hifadhi dhidi ya Sauli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:10-1Sam21:15\">1 Samweli 21:10–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam27:1-1Sam27:12\">27:1–12</a>). Walimzuia Daudi kupigana na watu wake mwenyewe (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam29:1-1Sam29:11\">1 Samweli 29:1–11</a>). Waliua Sauli na wanawe (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam31:1-1Sam31:13\">1 Samweli 31:1–13</a>), jambo lililomuwezesha Daudi kuwa mfalme. Hata hivyo, mwishowe, Wafilisti walipata hukumu ya Mungu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek25:15-Ezek25:17\">Ezekieli 25:15–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:6-Amos1:8\">Amosi 1:6–8</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen10:13-Gen10:14\">Mwanzo 10:13–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:1-Judg3:3\">Waamuzi 3:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:1-Judg16:31\">Waamuzi 13:1–16:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:1-1Sam6:18\">1 Samweli 5:1–6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:16-1Sam14:23\">13:16–14:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:10-1Sam21:15\">21:10–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:1-1Sam23:5\">23:1–5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:26-1Sam23:28\">26–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam31:1-1Sam31:10\">31:1–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:17-2Sam5:25\">2 Samweli 5:17–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:1\">8:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:15-2Sam21:22\">21:15–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:8\">2 Wafalme 18:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:10-2Chr17:11\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 17:10–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:16-2Chr21:17\">21:16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:6-2Chr26:7\">26:6–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:18-2Chr28:19\">28:18–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:6\">Isaya 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek25:15-Ezek25:17\">Ezekieli 25:15–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:6-Amos1:8\">Amosi 1:6–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:7\">9:7</a></p>",
